    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo in concours condition. This chassis retains its original 2JZ-GTE power plant, featuring the factory-spec sequential twin-turbocharger array for seamless torque delivery across the rev range. The Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, tactile engagement, paired with the original Torsen limited-slip differential. Every VIN tag is present and accounted for, reflecting a meticulously maintained example with zero mechanical modifications. The suspension geometry remains true to factory tolerances, and the forced induction system holds peak boost pressure with surgical precision. A rare opportunity to acquire a pristine, unmodified icon of Japanese engineering.",
